metadata.description: Aky Cats is a collection of 9,999 randomly generated and stylistically curated NFTs that bringing colour & creativity to the NFT space by supporting artists and spreading good vibeswith  traits and a custom image generation algorithm, each Aky Cats feels uniquely delicious. Aky Cats was created by an artist-led team, Aky Cats are in the public domain. feel free to use them in any way you want.
